        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://kartra.com"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you've been circling the idea of consolidating your marketing stack into one unified platform, this is the moment to pay attention. The team behind ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Kartra",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — Genesis Digital, the same crew that built WebinarJam and EverWebinar — has been shipping updates that make the platform significantly more capable for creators, coaches, and online businesses.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've been testing these features hands-on, and I want to walk you through what's new, why it matters, and whether Kartra deserves a spot in your workflow this year.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Let's get into it.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What Exactly Is Kartra?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Before the new stuff, a quick refresher.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Kartra is an all-in-one marketing platform that bundles together tools most online businesses cobble together from five or six separate subscriptions:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Sales pages and funnels",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " with drag-and-drop builders",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Email marketing",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " with automation sequences and tagging",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Membership sites",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " for courses and gated content",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Webinar and video hosting",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " integrated directly into the platform",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Helpdesk, calendars, and checkout",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — all native, no plugins required",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The pitch is simple: instead of paying for ClickFunnels + Mailchimp + Teachable + Calendly + Wistia, you get one login, one billing cycle, and everything talks to everything else.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "And now, that platform just got a serious upgrade.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "New and Highlighted Features Worth Your Attention",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here's what the Kartra team has been building. These aren't minor tweaks — they reshape how you can use the platform.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Smarter Webinar Integration with WebinarJam",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is the big one for anyone doing live or automated presentations.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Kartra's webinar capabilities have always been competent — you could host video content and replay pages without leaving the platform. But the latest updates tighten the integration with WebinarJam so that your webinar funnels, follow-up sequences, and purchase triggers all live inside a single workflow.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What does this look like in practice? You create a registration page in Kartra's page builder. Attendees sign up and are tagged automatically. During the webinar (hosted via WebinarJam), purchase buttons link directly to Kartra's checkout. After the event, Kartra sends targeted emails based on whether someone attended, watched the replay, or clicked a buy link.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "No Zapier. No manual CSV uploads. No duct tape.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/how-to-use-kartra-webinarjam"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you want to see exactly how this flow works step by step, our ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "tutorial on using Kartra with WebinarJam",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " breaks it down visually.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Enhanced Funnel Builder with Conditional Logic",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Kartra's funnel builder has always been visual and relatively intuitive. The recent update adds conditional branching — meaning your funnels can now adapt in real time based on user behavior.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Someone clicks a link in your email? They get Path A. Someone ignores three emails in a row? They get a re-engagement sequence instead. Someone purchases a $47 product? They're immediately offered a complementary $97 upsell.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This kind of adaptive funnel logic used to require tools like Deadline Funnel or custom scripts. Now it's baked into Kartra's native builder.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Improved Email Deliverability and Analytics",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Email marketers, this one's for you.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Kartra overhauled its sending infrastructure and added granular analytics to the email dashboard. You can now track:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Open rates segmented by device and time zone",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Click heatmaps showing which links get action",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Revenue per email (not just per campaign — per individual send)",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The deliverability improvements are harder to quantify from the outside, but early user reports suggest fewer messages landing in spam folders, especially for high-volume senders. Kartra has leaned into dedicated IP pools and better domain authentication tools.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/why-choose-kartra-webinarjam"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you're curious about the broader philosophy behind choosing Kartra over assembling tools individually, check out our deep dive on ",
            "marks": []
